  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891250/extras/7d3ea1128a4998fdcef83fdf6eb31d44.poster.avif?t=1770272700\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891250/extras/7d3ea1128a4998fdcef83fdf6eb31d44.webm?t=1770272700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891250/extras/7d3ea1128a4998fdcef83fdf6eb31d44.mp4?t=1770272700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>A <br><strong><i>STORY</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yasma escapes into new realities through video games and her art, adventuring through different aim training scenarios; she aims to be the best. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>ABOUT</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play through visually rich aim training levels portrayed as moments of escapism in Yasma’s world. Each collection of levels has their own stand alone narrative like Yasma saving the Princess in the handheld console game, Yasma’s drawings unveiling themselves through the levels and Yasma dance battling the characters from the console game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Like a traditional Aim Trainer, there will be varying familiar aim training scenarios you can play through. There will also be a few unconventional levels that cater more to the story! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>FEATURES:</i></strong>- 3 Story Modes<br>- Unique Aim Training Levels<br>- Mini Games<br>- An Original Soundtrack</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Header art by @mizrii_ (twitter) <3<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891250/extras/2c640737d0614df58320633f846f67ac.poster.avif?t=1770272700\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891250/extras/2c640737d0614df58320633f846f67ac.webm?t=1770272700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891250/extras/2c640737d0614df58320633f846f67ac.mp4?t=1770272700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891250/extras/7d3ea1128a4998fdcef83fdf6eb31d44.poster.avif?t=1770272700\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891250/extras/7d3ea1128a4998fdcef83fdf6eb31d44.webm?t=1770272700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891250/extras/7d3ea1128a4998fdcef83fdf6eb31d44.mp4?t=1770272700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>A <br><strong><i>STORY</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yasma escapes into new realities through video games and her art, adventuring through different aim training scenarios; she aims to be the best. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>ABOUT</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play through visually rich aim training levels portrayed as moments of escapism in Yasma’s world. Each collection of levels has their own stand alone narrative like Yasma saving the Princess in the handheld console game, Yasma’s drawings unveiling themselves through the levels and Yasma dance battling the characters from the console game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Like a traditional Aim Trainer, there will be varying familiar aim training scenarios you can play through. There will also be a few unconventional levels that cater more to the story! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>FEATURES:</i></strong>- 3 Story Modes<br>- Unique Aim Training Levels<br>- Mini Games<br>- An Original Soundtrack</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Header art by @mizrii_ (twitter) <3<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891250/extras/2c640737d0614df58320633f846f67ac.poster.avif?t=1770272700\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891250/extras/2c640737d0614df58320633f846f67ac.webm?t=1770272700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891250/extras/2c640737d0614df58320633f846f67ac.mp4?t=1770272700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
